its has the kbf(knock back factor).thats sumthin i'm pretty sure some-1 came up with b-4.well its a interactive enviroment.in my game all spells will have kbf, so when you read the spell stats it reads how far you'll go back when when you use it and vice versa 4 the enemy or friend.so this means you'll be able to knock people through walls,fences, and the ground. thats y my rpg's a real time rpg. and it does the matrix....you can run off walls and attack,dodge attacks, do impossible moves, all with the matrix feature. also it will have voice over on everything(like shenmue).and last you can mix spells,interact with your enviroment(ex-you knock someone into a gun shop.you can use a gun from the shop)and live out a real life.<br>
